asset.title: 2003-2007 Ford F250, F350, F450, F550 Super Duty and Excursion 6.0L Diesel Air Intake Installation
asset.description:
See how easy it is to add more performance to your 2003-2007 Ford F250, F350, F450, F550 Super Duty and Excursion 6.0L Diesel with this K&N air intake system. 

http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=57-2546-1

This intake system created an estimated gain of 15.53 horsepower at 3426 RPM.
